{"tid":1393072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 基督/天主教徒 禮賓府星期六要人","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T02:15:25.000Z","uid":56052,"like":134,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"9c296f1867915b1f2beaf883ee6331a843da75c3","tid":1393072,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:20:35.000Z","msg":"禮賓府外敬拜活動已經舉辦到第四個禮拜，喺其他義士/公務員/車長都走出嚟嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">作為社會上其中一個大群體，又點可以放棄發聲？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n聖經教導我地要作光，但喺光明下發光係冇用㗎，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真正需要光嘅地方係黑暗</span></span><br />\n如果你仿效耶穌嘅樣式，請你喺翻教會以外嘅時間走出嚟，嚟當權者嘅門外呼求主嘅公義降臨<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就好似耶穌走人聖殿驅走商人嘅私慾，痛楚罵掌權嘅法利賽人，用佢嘅生命奉獻為公義發聲</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當大家用自己嘅方式爭取公義嘅時候，我地更加要企出嚟對準焦點，對準當權者發聲<br />\n<br />\n請勤記，教會唔係建築物。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">教會，係由你和我，用身體、用上帝嘅話語，以主為中心所建立。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要你企係我地嘅群體當中，誠心相信主會帶來公義和救屬，你就係我地一份子!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHsReVs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHsReVs.jpg&h=436136da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與神同行<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/walkingwithgod\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwalkingwithgod&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl58F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=cc217bcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/walkingwithgod</a>"},{"pid":"951b63caf3a9fd8d0630d5cadba9622a5185614e","tid":1393072,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"勿理巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2f96c681b0a99297fe4fcc568d11dbcbab7178","tid":1393072,"uid":270428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:22:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ef5a